data.title: L. Sprague De Camp
data.meta_description: L. Sprague De Camp. Additional Crew: Conan, der Barbar. L. Sprague De Camp was born on 27 November 1907 in New York City, New York, USA. He is known for Conan, der Barbar (1982), Conan der Zerstörer (1984) and Kull, der Eroberer (1997). He was married to Catherine Adelaide Crook deCamp. He died on 6 November 2000 in Plano, Texas, USA.
